title: BREAKING: Three suspected ISIS terrorists arrested in mosque raid
text:
BREAKING: Three suspected ISIS terrorists arrested in mosque raid BREAKING: Three suspected ISIS terrorists arrested in mosque raid THREE suspected ISIS terrorists have been arrested at the Berlin mosque used by Christmas market attacker Anis Amri. PUBLISHED: 22:13, Tue, Jan 31, 2017 | UPDATED: 22:23, Tue, Jan 31, 2017 
Prosecutors said they were examining links between the there men and ISIS connections in Syria and Iraq. 
They said there was no evidence to suggest a terror attack on Germany was imminent.
